import { Stack } from "@mui/material"
import WhiteTypography from "./WhiteTypography"
import LocationOnIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LocationOn';
import EmailIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Email';
import PhoneIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Phone';
import "../App.css"

export default function ContactDetails() {
    return (
        <Stack spacing={3} style={{alignItems: "start"}}>
            <WhiteTypography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div" style={{ marginBottom: "3rem" }}>
                Contact Details
            </WhiteTypography>
            <Stack direction="row">
                <LocationOnIcon style={{ color: "white", marginRight: "3rem" }} className="mx-auto" />
                <WhiteTypography gutterBottom variant="h6" component="div" style={{ marginBottom: "3rem" }}>
                    Location
                </WhiteTypography>
            </Stack>
            <Stack direction="row">
                <EmailIcon style={{ color: "white", marginRight: "3rem" }} className="mx-auto" />
                <WhiteTypography gutterBottom variant="h6" component="div" style={{ marginBottom: "3rem" }}>
                    Email
                </WhiteTypography>
            </Stack>
            <Stack direction="row">
                <PhoneIcon style={{ color: "white", marginRight: "3rem" }} className="mx-auto" />
                <WhiteTypography gutterBottom variant="h6" component="div" style={{ marginBottom: "3rem" }}>
                    Phone
                </WhiteTypography>
            </Stack>
        </Stack>
    )
}
